#: wildmage/tra/english/text.tra:69999
msgid ""
"My dear friend Gorion,\n"
"\n"
"be careful on your departure, there's a Wild Mage hanging about outside the walls of Candlekeep. His intentions are unknown; once you left the keep, better hit the trail straightaway.\n"
"\n"
"E."
msgstr ""
"Mon cher ami Gorion,\n"
"\n"
"Sois attentif lors de ton départ, il y a un entropiste qui traine à l'extérieur des murs de Château-Suif. Ses intentions sont inconnues ; il serait préférable de prendre directement la route dès que vous aurez quitté le château.\n"
"\n"
"E."
